The girl walked uneasily through the forest. She
had never ventured this far from the village
before.

However, the girl had a purpose. That's why, even
though she was scared, she continued on.

The place the girl was taught about long ago...
Her destination must be here. But... is it really
here? The girl looks around uneasily.

Before she knew it────── it really appeared right
in front of her. It was incredibly large...
shining in gold... magnificent... a dragon...!
